quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Yaqeenan hum ney iss say pehlay ibrahim ko iss ki samajh boojh bakhshi thi aur hum iss kay ehwaal say ba-khoobi waqif thay
  21,52,Jabkay uss ney apney baap say aur pani qom say kaha kay yeh moortiyan jin kay tum mujawar bann bethay ho kiya hain
  21,53,Sab ney jawab diya kay hum ney apnay baap dada ko enhi ki ibadat kertay huye paya
  21,54,Aap ney farmaya! Phir to tum aur tumharay baap dada sabhi yaqeenan khulli gumrahi mein mubtila rahey
  21,55,Kehnay lagay kiya aap humaray pass sach much haq laye hain ya yun hi mazaq ker rahey hain
  21,56,Aap ney farmaya nahi dar-haqeeqat tum sab ka perwerdigar to woh hai jo aasmano aur zamin ka malik hai jiss ney unehn peda kiya hai mein to issi baat ka gawah aur qaeel hun
  21,57,Aur Allah ki qasam mein tumharay inn maboodon kay sath jab tum alehda peeth pher ker chal do gay aik chaal chalon ga
  21,58,Pus uss ney unn sab kay tukray tukray ker diye haan sirf baray butt ko chor diya yeh bhi iss liye kay woh sab uss ki taraf hi loten
  21,59,Kehney lagay kay humaray khudaon kay sath yeh kiss ney kiya? Aisa shaks to yaqeenan zalimon mein say hai
  21,60,Bolay hum ney aik no-jawan ko innk a tazkara kertay huye suna tha jissay ibrahim (alh-e-salam) kaha jata hai
  21,61,Sab ney kaha acha ussay majmay mein logon ki nigahon kay samney lao takay sab dekhen
  21,62,Kehnay lagay! Aey ibrahim (alh-e-salam) kiya tu ney hi humaray khudaon kay sath yeh harkat ki hai
  21,63,Aap ney jawab diya bulkay iss kaam ko inn kay baray ney kiya hai tum apney khudaon say hi pooch lo agar yeh boltay chaltay hon
  21,64,Pus yeh log apney dilon mein qaeel hogaye aur kehney lagay waqaee zalim to tum hi ho
  21,65,Phir apney saron kay bal ondhay hogaye (aur kehnay lagay kay) yeh to tujhay bhi maloom hai kay yeh bolney chaalney walay nahi
  21,66,Allah kay khalil ney ussi waqt farmaya afsos! Kiya tum Allah kay ilawa unn ki ibadat kertay ho jo na tumhen kuch bhi nafa phoncha saken na nuksan
  21,67,Tuff hai tum per aur inn per jin ki tum Allah kay siwa ibadat kertay ho. Kiya tumhen itni si aqal bhi nahi
  21,68,Kehney lagay issay jala do aur apney khudaon ki madad kero agar tumhen kuch kerna hi hai
  21,69,Hum ney farma diya aey aag! Tu thandi parr jaa aur ibrahim (alh-e-salam) kay liye salamti (aur aaram ki cheez) bann jaa
  21,70,Go unhon ney ibrahim (alh-e-salam) ka bura chaha lekin hum ney unhen nakaam bana diya
  21,71,Aur hum ibrahim aur loot ko bacha ker uss zamin ki taraf ley chalay jiss mein hum ney tamam jahan walon kay liye barkat rakhi thi
  21,72,Aur hum ney ussay ishaq ata farmaya aur yaqoob iss per mazeed. Aur her aik ko hum ney saleh banaya
  21,73,Aur hum ney unehn paishwa bana diya kay humaray hukum say logon ki rehbari keren aur hum ney unn ki taraf nek kaamon kay kerney aur namazon kay qaeem rakhney aur zakat denay ki wahee (talqeen) ki aur woh sab kay sab humaray ibadat guzaar banday thay
  21,74,Hum ney loot (alh-e-salam) ko bhi hukum aur ilm diya aur ussay uss basti say nijat di jahan kay log ganday kaamon mein mubtila thay. Aur thay bhi woh bad-tareen gunehgaar
  21,75,Aur hum ney loot (alh-e-salam) ko apni rehmat mein dakhil ker liya bey shak woh neko kaar logon mein say tha
  21,76,Nooh kay uss waqt ko yaad kijiye jabkay uss ney iss say pehlay dua ki hum ney uss ki dua qabool farmaee aur ussay aur uss kay ghar walon ko baray karb say nijat di
  21,77,Aur jo log humari aayaton ko jhutla rahey thay unn kay muqablay mein hum ney uss ki madad ki yaqeenan woh buray log thay pus hum ney unn sab ko dobo diya
  21,78,Aur dawood (alh-e-salam) aur suleman (alh-e-salam) ko yaad kijiye jabkay woh khet kay moamlay mein faisla ker rahey thay kay kuch logon ki bakriyan raat ko iss mein char chug gaee thin aur unn kay faislay mein hum mojood thay
  21,79,Hum ney iss ka sahih faisla suleman ko samjha diya. Haan her aik ko hum ney hukum-o-ilm dey rakha tha aur dawood kay tabey hum ney pahar ker diye thay jo tasbeeh kertay thay aur parind bhi. Hum kerney walay hi thay
  21,80,Aur hum ney ussay tumharay liye libaas bananey ki kaari gari sikhaee takay laraee kay zarar say tumhara bachao ho. Kiya tum shukar guzar bano gay
  21,81,Hum ney tund-o-tez hawa ko suleman (alh-e-salam) kay tabey ker diya jo uss kay farmaan kay mutabiq uss zamin ki taraf chalti thi jahan hum ney barkat dey rakhi thi aur hum her cheez say ba-khabar aur dana hain
  21,82,Issi tarah say boht say shayateen bhi hum ney uss kay tabey kiye thay jo uss kay farmaan say ghotay lagatay thay aur iss kay siwa bhi boht say kaam kiya kertay thay inn kay nigehbaan hum hi thay